  "keyFeatures": [
    "Multi-language code editor with syntax highlighting for 20+ languages",
    "AI assistant with 30+ tool actions (analyze, fix, refactor, generate, run)",
    "Browser-native terminal powered by WebContainers (Node.js in the browser)",
    "Arduino sketch editor with breadboard simulation and board flashing",
    "Scratch programming environment with .sb3 import support",
    "3D/CAD editor with text-to-3D AI generation from 6 providers",
    "Integrated Git version control with branching and import from GitHub/GitLab/Bitbucket",
    "Project saving, forking, starring, and subdomain publishing",
    "BYOK (bring-your-own-key) support for OpenAI, Anthropic, Gemini, DeepSeek, and more",
    "Media editors for audio, video, images, and Office documents (Word, Excel, PowerPoint)",
    "Real-time collaboration via Supabase",
    "Workflow automation with reusable, named run/build/test tasks"
  ],
